  "2321250": {
    "name": "A Corgi's Cozy Hike",
    "steam_appid": 2321250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/c1ab34a9476c4cc81b67353670d4cc1a.avif?t=1763842689\" width=1000 height=332 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become a SUPERCORGI!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <i>Corgi Butt Power</i> to use corgi superpowers to <i>climb</i> and <i>soar</i> and prove  stubby legs can't stop you on your hike to <i>Serenity Summit!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play With a Friend!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Paws Menu, enable <strong>Splitscreen Couch Co-op </strong>and give a controller or keyboard to Player 2<strong>!</strong> Explore the world and collect bones together!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Corgi Unleashed!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a seamless open-world! Five regions await a curious pup. Freely travel between them, filling out your stamp card with collectibles you find along your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/ebe0a61f3c062ae551001539ab7aefc0.poster.avif?t=1763842689\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/ebe0a61f3c062ae551001539ab7aefc0.webm?t=1763842689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/ebe0a61f3c062ae551001539ab7aefc0.mp4?t=1763842689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Everything!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your own path around the island! So many secrets are hidden in the nooks and crannies of Grico Island. Everything is optional. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/54ee3b2512379036cc23671a8c504178.avif?t=1763842689\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras_big/54ee3b2512379036cc23671a8c504178.avif?t=1763842689 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit <strong>Ancient Corgi Statues </strong>to learn abilities like <strong>Climbing</strong> and <strong>Gliding</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect <i>Corgi Butt Power</i> to increase your<i> </i><strong>Climbing Stamina</strong> to reach higher areas!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue dogs and bring them to your <strong>Animal Sanctuary.</strong> You can visit them and bring them toys later!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mark your territory</strong> by finding <i>Fire Hydrants</i> to fill out the map!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dig up</strong> treats and toys! Use treats to buy <strong>Costumes</strong>!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relax at Cozy Spots</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/3094041ccbee5acde1d6f83577e05843.poster.avif?t=1763842689\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/3094041ccbee5acde1d6f83577e05843.webm?t=1763842689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/3094041ccbee5acde1d6f83577e05843.mp4?t=1763842689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the serenity of the island’s natural beauty at special cozy spots. Put your controller down and delight in the peaceful music and animations. Maybe now’s a good time to do that work you've been putting off? Or be inspired to do some journaling or drawing!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet Friends!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/ec3934eb3d18fd089b4b65613759000f.poster.avif?t=1763842689\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/ec3934eb3d18fd089b4b65613759000f.webm?t=1763842689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/ec3934eb3d18fd089b4b65613759000f.mp4?t=1763842689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're man's best friend for a reason. Help islanders with their problems, just like dogs do! Who knows? You might even earn some Corgi Butt Power?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cute Costumes!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want Hats, Scarfs, Shirts, or Capes? We've got them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras/674a0172357c95dde788dcbf6b536f94.avif?t=1763842689\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321250/extras_big/674a0172357c95dde788dcbf6b536f94.avif?t=1763842689 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What type of corgi will <strong>you</strong> be? Tri-color?  Blue Merle? Hint: you can change your Corgi Coat using a secret method in the intro area (The Doggy Bowl). Can you figure it out? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can you pet the dog?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Well... you ARE the dog! Let people pet YOU! You can <i>boop</i> other dogs you find, too!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Our Mission</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We make games that make a difference. We wanted to give people a fun, relaxing way to help real dogs. And, 10% of all proceeds donate to shelters to sponsor rescue dogs! We appreciate your support :) We also intend for our games to heal players. Life is stressful. Be a dog for a few hours, it helps!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow our Scalisco Developer Steam Page </strong>so you know when we release more games that help us donate to help animals and other causes. <i>(Click our developer name, Scalisco, at the top of the page!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our wholesome community on Discord (check the links on the side of the page).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit  to see our corgi merch and mobile games that also help us donate to animal shelters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for playing!</p>",
